  "text": "Hygienic measures, such as correct disposal of the hunting carcasses and carcass remains, should become compulsory in every country and for every hunting modality [CITATION_1] ). However, research to assess the true risks of such management in every particular situation is needed in favour of the conservation of some wildlife species that usually survive very fragmentally and at the edge of their possibilities in Europe.",
